comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-13T22:19:48.147Z",codex-root,"Duplicate check 2026-07-14: all-status searches for GH-548, id_prefix rename, workspace prefix migration, and prefix reference rewrite found no canonical item. GitHub issue #548 is canonical external evidence; this item is deliberately left open and unclaimed."
body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/548\n\nThis is backlog tracking only in the current immutable-history/read implementation lane. It belongs to the existing schema-evolution program rather than a new migration subsystem."
